Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.55,0:22:13.70,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(315,478)\fs29\fsp1}心中的深处闪烁着光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.92,0:22:19.90,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(315,478)\fs29\fsp1}无法舍弃对你的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.90,0:22:24.78,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(315,478)\fs29\fsp1}只能静静的闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.24,0:22:28.99,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(315,478)\fs29\fsp1}过去的些许小事也好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.99,0:22:34.70,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(315,478)\fs29\fsp1}极为平常的言语也好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.41,0:22:39.25,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(315,478)\fs29\fsp1}当想起之时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.25,0:22:44.38,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(315,478)\fs29\fsp1}泪水就不知不觉的流出
